{"tid":496069,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Zemo算唔算係MCU最成功嘅反派？","createTime":"2017-12-11T10:30:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-12T07:56:22.000Z","uid":86587,"like":19,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"630209258fbedd8cad77413bcc897db711f79ea5","tid":496069,"uid":86587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T10:30:09.000Z","msg":"首先，佢報仇嘅原因容易被觀眾理解同情，作為一個普通人，最珍視嘅家人因為奧創而冚家鏟，始作俑者tony stark拯救完世界就走咗人，唔需要承擔責任，係人都會唔憤氣喇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其次，佢係唯一一個成功達到目標嘅反派。佢好清楚要打敗復仇者嘅方法就係令佢地分裂內鬥，如果有共同敵人佢地肯定會放下仇恨聯手抗敵，所以果斷殺死5個冬兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最後佢比人監禁，看似計劃失敗，實際上復仇者已經係名存實亡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然Zemo出場時間唔夠十分鐘，但無論喺演技，動機同策劃都大勝同期戲份超多嘅lex luthor，算係一個非常成功反派，大家點睇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"211227d86c4e03516bb440c38967189260d72807","tid":496069,"uid":2861,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T10:43:25.000Z","msg":"感覺太多巧合，而且戲份唔多幾可惜，但的確係個好反派<br />\n同埋我鐘意禿鷹同starlord 老豆"},{"pid":"3d4c76ae36e84f3fca547289fc04769b5bb2ba50","tid":496069,"uid":16635,"like":6,"dislike":5,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T10:45:06.000Z","msg":"巴打成日開認真mcu post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我覺得loki成功啲 始終出嘅時間多好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 人物立體好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但係比起同期lex luthor無論動機同手法都高質好多<br />\nlex luthor嘅細個比老豆虐待無神救佢真係好撚on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"http://78.media.tumblr.com/fd8ba868c5d3377c18a88f809c57af5f/tumblr_oavcjkqvbO1vsd1kxo1_500.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https: